orthy of such a title, some of the quests are a joke…nothing epic about them. I considered the Cleric Res-Clicker somewhat epic, until I found out that one of the quest NPCs that made it tough was actually broken resulting in a more difficult encounter than was intended(that elemental thing originally had a 1000 point AE). Then the final step was a joke.<br>
<br>
Hail a dragon_I_killed_at_level_45<br>
