There were others that were way too easy as well. The Freebringer, you can do almost all of it with 1-2 people and the Monk epic which can be started and completed in a day(assuming you already had items that were available months before epics were implemented). They didn’t put any time or consideration into balancing the difficulty associated with each class’s epic, that’s why there were 20 Ragebringers, Shaman spears and Res-clickers before there was 1 mage/wizard epic.<br>
<br>
